  <description>Seta 4–11 mm, straight.  Capsule, when mature, broadly ovoid, 3–7 mm and nearly as wide, rich, glossy, chestnut brown, upper face flattened and sharply differen-tiated from lower face by a dark brown ridge, oblique or nearly at right angles to seta.  Spores 6–8 µm.</description>
  <phenology>Capsules mature late spring–fall.</phenology>
